OL,5, Body worn cameras are being used by a  
OL,6, high street shop to curb rising levels 
OL,7, of theft and violence in its stores.   
OL,9,FJohn Lewis has given its staff bodycams
OL,10,Fand "de-escalation" training to diffuse
OL,11,Ftensions when shoppers react angrily.  
OL,13,FThe Welsh Retail Consortium (WRC) said 
OL,14,Fviolence towards staff in Cardiff      
OL,15,Fbetween 2021 and 2022 had risen by 30% 
OL,16,Fwhile shoplifting had spiked by 68%.   
OL,18,FThe Home Office said it had invested a 
OL,19,Frecord amount into policing but        
OL,20,Fretailers have demanded tougher laws.  
